Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

CRITICAL BUG FIX: mcp_server quality gate was fail-OPEN (silent allow on
ImportError). Now fail-CLOSED via governance facade.

New module ao_kernel/governance.py:
- check_policy(): policy validation with required_fields/blocked/limits
- evaluate_quality(): quality gate evaluation — DENY on error, never silent allow
- quality_summary(): structured gate result summary
- QualityGateResult dataclass

Changes:
- mcp_server.py: handle_quality_gate() now uses ao_kernel.governance facade
  instead of direct src.orchestrator import (fixes bypass)
- No more ImportError → allow path (was: lines 254-262)

Design decision (Codex CNS-20260413-011):
- ao_kernel.governance is the governance facade (not llm)
- Fail-closed: gate error → DENY, not allow
- MCP server is transport adapter, governance logic in facade

16 new tests, 240 total passing.

